transcript.sentence: The show opens with an aerial view of the town of adventure bay. Then six dogs raced toward the tower, filled with their dog houses.
Their owner rider calls the dogs away from playing soccer to come back to their lookout.
As the dog's names are called, each slide down the slide and into their dog houses, which turn into vehicles.
Their owner then jumps onto a 4 wheeler and leaves the six dogs into the city of adventure bay.
It cuts to a rescue of the dog, saving a young boy from a cliff
with each of their special gear, like fire department equipment. Please tools in a helicopter.
As the video ends, it advertises more nick Junior videos on their APP.

audio_descriptions.notes:
0:00 The show opens with an ariel view of the town of Adventure Bay. Then six dogs race towards a tower filled with their dog houses. 

0:08 Their owner, Ryder, calls the dogs away from paying soccer to come back to their lookout. 

0:13 As the dogs names are called, they each slide down the slide and into their dog houses, which turn into vehicles. 

0:20 Their owner jumps onto a four wheeler and leads the six dogs into the city of adventure Bay.

0:26 Then the video cuts to a rescue of the dogs saving a young boy from a cliff with each of their special gear like, fire department equipment, police tools, and a helicopter. 

0:35 As the video ends it advertises more Nick Jr. videos on their app.
